title: Sigh
text: 1) If you are going to have 4 or more obtainable surfers an event make the runs easier especially when there are 2 different challenge runs (timed and veins/lava) it’s too much to do 2 10mil runs every event on top of grinding out tokens and event coins. 2) Unlock runs again so we don’t have to kill ourselves in game to progress through challenge runs. 3) Give more benefits to players who buy items. (Ex: Top ups, expand the collections feature) 4) If you are going to sell a character from a previous event sell their board as well. 5) Add a friends feature where we can see how much they have run that week. Let us have a profile where we can display our favorite surfers and our best runs. (Ex: Mario Kart Tour) 6) Add something that shows us how many tiers/stages we have completed for tokens/challenge runs WHILE we are running so we don’t have to remember. 7) Add stories. (Ex: Twisted Wonderlands “Chats” and “Vignettes” feature) Expand the lore of characters. After x amount of miles run with a character or the obtainment of certain character outfits you unlock a story or an interaction that reveals something about them. Make us care about the surfers outside of the main group.
